No. 09-1328. Keith Smith, Warden, Petitioner v. Robert S. Vasquez. 562 U.S. 946, 131 S. Ct. 83,

178 L. Ed. 2d 241,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7828. October 4, 2010.
